Installation instruction for source and binary tar.gz package
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. FreeBSD
~~~~~~~~~~
a. From source package

   Build and install:
   $ tar -xzf cmmapi-0.1.tar.gz
   $ ./configure
   $ make
   # make install

   Remove:
   # make uninstall

2. Linux
~~~~~~~~
a. From source package

   Build and install:
   $ tar -xzf cmmapi-0.1.tar.gz
   $ ./configure
   $ make
   # make install

   Remove:
   # make uninstall

b. From binary package

   Install:
   # tar -xzf cmmapi-0.1-i586.tar.gz
   # cd cmmapi
   # ./create_links
            or
   # tar -xzf cmmapi-0.1-i586.tar.gz
   # cd cmmapi
   # ./install

   Remove:
   # cd cmmapi
   # ./remove_links
   # cd ..
   # rm -r cmmapi
            or
   # /opt/cmmapi/uninstall

